title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Complete The Gangbanger Robbery and Claim the Übermacht Cypher
content:
Yusuf Amir’s cousin Jamal has got an in with Ballas OG-turned-podcaster King Tiny — who’s currently being held in the Mission Row LSPD precinct. Find a way to infiltrate the police station, rescue King Tiny, and steal the prized Übermacht Cypher (Sports), with the option to claim this unique ride as your own.

Get started by buying your own Salvage Yard from the Maze Bank Foreclosures, then use the Salvage Yard’s computer and Planning Wall to select a target and launch your operations.
